.76},{"word":"God","start":306.76,"end":307.84},{"word":"thank","start":307.9,"end":308.88},{"word":"God","start":308.88,"end":309.74},{"word":"thank","start":309.78,"end":310.76},{"word":"God","start":310.76,"end":312.22},{"word":"thank","start":312.3,"end":314.04},{"word":"God","start":314.04,"end":315.06},{"word":"For","start":315.06,"end":315.46},{"word":"my","start":315.46,"end":315.88},{"word":"last","start":315.88,"end":319.38},{"word":"first","start":319.38,"end":321.4},{"word":"kiss","start":321.4,"end":324.1}],"lines":[{"text":"The seasons of life","start":13.08,"end":17.72},{"text":"they turn like pages Some burn fast some last for ages You","start":18.12,"end":23.62},{"text":"love you lose you learn to pray You never think it'll break","start":23.62,"end":28.4},{"text":"that way You hold on tight to what you miss Never knowing","start":28.4,"end":33.7},{"text":"heaven's got a better script Than out of nowhere grace walks in","start":33.7,"end":39.66},{"text":"A fire in her eyes and peace in her kiss Thank God","start":39.66,"end":44.72},{"text":"for my last first kiss Struck like lightning","start":44.72,"end":51.88},{"text":"felt like this Heaven opened","start":53.46,"end":58.26},{"text":"time stood still All my broken roads led to her will","start":59.94,"end":68.48},{"text":"My true love came no doubt","start":69.32,"end":72.28},{"text":"no guess My life was waiting for that kiss If forever had","start":73.16,"end":77.88},{"text":"a name","start":77.88,"end":78.68},{"text":"it'd be this Thank God for my last first kiss","start":79.1,"end":87.22},{"text":"Some storms teach you who you are Some scars shine like guiding","start":90.56,"end":96.22},{"text":"stars","start":96.22,"end":97.08},{"text":"Every tear that once fell down Led me straight to my queen's","start":97.48,"end":103.46},{"text":"crown The hurt is gone the joy runs deep She's a promise","start":103.46,"end":107.9},{"text":"my soul gets to keep When she smiles the whole world chills","sta